replyTime":"2019-01-29T15:56:50.000Z","msg":"11點半啦"},{"pid":"f95a5f735cf7adebf166fbae2124142190fd828c","tid":1000293,"uid":59224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"accd8c9d5189faa946939e3feabe72843feb2894","tid":1000293,"uid":42835,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T12:53:30.000Z","msg":"1130出 支持請正皮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T16:07:18.000Z","msg":"明早1130？"},{"pid":"b63880b72b278c772e0b5e19d656eb1a0db8e5cc","tid":1000293,"uid":42835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T16:17:29.000Z","msg":"出了。"},{"pid":"985d2b664cfeb241bbe931f205f509a131cf957a","tid":1000293,"uid":227414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b63880b72b278c772e0b5e19d656eb1a0db8e5cc","tid":1000293,"uid":42835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T16:17:29.000Z","msg":"出了。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T16:27:23.000Z","msg":"出左係邊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"399405c4e1ea23cd1b61f52d04340e271c9eb0ca","tid":1000293,"uid":200550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T16:46:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3284926169cdeca47ca3ec97e3fbe926855ea8ad","tid":1000293,"uid":42835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T17:25:42.000Z","msg":"今天只是比平日特別一點的便服日。<br />\n原本我以為。<br />\n只是誰料到，我簡直是大錯特錯⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n「呀！」<br />\n我用力揉著凌亂的短髮，對著鏡子喃喃細語。<br />\n鏡裡邊映影著床上橫攤著一疊疊懶散的衣裝。<br />\n「該穿那一件呢⋯⋯」<br />\n<em>好煩惱。<br />\n</em><br />\n就這樣，不經不覺過了出門的時間。<br />\n「噢，快要遲到了⋯⋯」<br />\n我隨手拿起那條白棠花碎長裙，然後焦急地走回學校。<br />\n<br />\n在校前那十字路口，竟然遠遠聽到有人在吟詩：<br />\n「忙下去，捱下去。但一不小心⋯⋯」<br />\n大概是那些晨早起床沒事幹的大叔吧。<br />\n急步走過好了。<br />\n<br />\n「哎呀！」<br />\n可是我還是和這個奇怪大叔撞在一起了⋯⋯<br />\n<em>怎麼辦⋯⋯<br />\n他好像是閉著眼的，是盲人嗎？<br />\n我會被罵嗎？<br />\n今天真是一個糟糕的一天！<br />\n</em>我就這樣坐在地上，心裡暗暗擔心著。<br />\n<br />\n「你⋯⋯沒事嗎？對不起。」<br />\n想不到眼前才不是甚麼盲俠，而是個身穿白襯衣、綠色褲的男生。<br />\n他先是有點害羞地咬著唇，然後高居臨下地向我伸出了右手。<br />\n很可愛⋯⋯很紳子⋯⋯<br />\n我故意放輕全身的力，軟棉棉地好讓他把我拉起。<br />\n<br />\n「哎，不是呢，我也有錯，我太衝忙呢。」我用盡全身的力拍去裙上的灰塵。<br />\n<em>我的裙子污了⋯⋯<br />\n</em>抬頭發現，他就這樣一動不動，一臉茫然地看著我。<br />\n<br />\n「對了，我叫可嵐⋯⋯」<br />\n<em>等一下，我幹嘛在介紹自己呢！<br />\n瘋了瘋了，這個世界瘋了。<br />\n我也瘋了。<br />\n我要走！快點走！離開現場！<br />\n</em><br />\nA：到附近便利店<br />\nB：到小賣部附近<br />\nC：回課室<br />\nD：到操場附近"},{"pid":"f08224871451df38bf0860885f873adacbc1a301","tid":1000293,"uid":56818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T17:33:58.000Z","msg":"A"},{"pid":"6338ae5e8ce8d21eb3b790f5491a3c0cdd5d5954","tid":1000293,"uid":234086,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T17:53:03.000Z","msg":"笑話一則<br />\n可蘭M到<br />\n變左可蘭經"},{"pid":"0300db2e29e736a95374411ca6f4254f6d5c89f2","tid":1000293,"uid":42835,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6338ae5e8ce8d21eb3b790f5491a3c0cdd5d5954","tid":1000293,"uid":234086,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T17:53:03.000Z","msg":"笑話一則<br />\n可蘭M到<br />\n變左可蘭經"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T17:58:00.000Z","msg":"尊重"},{"pid":"b2cf96b028b8f4e443c402a8dd7c2d34618e3a05","tid":1000293,"uid":40450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T23:27:30.000Z","msg":"C"},{"pid":"376f07b46f703ca8160749f3610ab0eb6a89da67","tid":1000293,"uid":223437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T00:59:22.000Z","msg":"C"},{"pid":"0ddcf31fd38bcef95705e769c8d2068373b3127d","tid":1000293,"uid":129142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T02:00:31.000Z","msg":"C <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95a21c3f75eef53e960b4c0a782c268d2f098f4f","tid":1000293,"uid":116614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T02:12:05.000Z","msg":"回憶都要選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7cda290ea62b77976d9113adedb94930402d482","tid":1000293,"uid":38395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95a21c3f75eef53e960b4c0a782c268d2f098f4f","tid":1000293,"uid":116614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T02:12:05.000Z","msg":"回憶都要選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T03:59:05.000Z","msg":"如果唔係點拖劇情"},{"pid":"8619cef046d6dee22f67f8950ad1a8f7f087ae61","tid":1000293,"uid":42835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95a21c3f75eef53e960b4c0a782c268d2f098f4f","tid":1000293,"uid":116614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T02:12:05.000Z","msg":"回憶都要選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T10:06:57.000Z","msg":"諗諗下回憶飛快D算，都唔係好影響劇情。"},{"pid":"6c70de6d98c7fd9a5ba729b38f27487e1d43f98a","tid":1000293,"uid":42835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T10:07:31.000Z","msg":"請繼續支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e2e8be95ed9ca17a916a54f16d580c0495a43f5","tid":1000293,"uid":42835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T10:26:37.000Z","msg":"幾經波折，我回到了課室。<br />\n人來人往之間，我找不著自己的位置。<br />\n那種感覺就像周圍都是彩色的，就只剩下自己灰色的格格不入。<br />\n歡笑閒雜聲之間，我走過講台，卻有數位女同學在圍著聊天。<br />\n「不好意思，請借借。」我很想說。<br />\n可是連這句說話都不敢說的我，就只有默默地站在她們的身後。<br />\n<br />\n「呀。」突然面前的長髮女孩仰後大笑，踏了我的腳一下。<br />\n我立刻揮揮手就走過，就像是我做錯一樣。<br />\n「不好意⋯⋯」所以她也理想當然不道歉了。<br />\n<br />\n我坐到窗邊的後座，看著晴朗的藍天，聯想到身上白棠花碎長裙，只有一陣憂鬱。<br />\n我抬頭看看周圍，坐是空空的座位，沒有眼晴的人⋯⋯<br />\n我攤開雙手，手掌輕微擦損。<br />\n原來右膝也擦傷了。我用力把長裙向下拉。<br />\n我疊起雙手墊著頭臥在桌上，就這樣裝作休息吧⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n突然，在老師說話期間，有個人走了進來。"},{"pid":"be3fed72c563d83a17bbadcc0b951af02a79c00f","tid":1000293,"uid":180178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T14:02:39.000Z","msg":"今日仲有冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}